gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 116, Knicks 102
gameRecap.excerpt: Boston defeats New York, 116-102. For Boston, Jaylen Brown led the way with 30 points and 8 rebounds aided by Kristaps Porzingis (22 points, four rebounds, four assists) and Jayson Tatum (19 points, six rebounds, six assists, two steals). Jalen Brunson led the way with 34 points and nine assists with Josh Hart adding 16 points, eight rebounds, and six assists for New York in the losing effort. Boston wins and improves to 45-12 on the season, while New York moves to 34-23 with the loss.
